{"tid":2124500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★市民全副裝備行街市 但徒手拿起鮮魚 亦有人輪流觸摸瓜菜","createTime":"2020-07-25T12:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T15:43:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fefbd6c3cff95c7e456325d3ffc58d0f055e50a8","tid":2124500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:09:22.000Z","msg":"近日慈雲山有多宗確診個案，位於距離不遠的黃大仙雙鳳街街市，亦有多名市民如常買餸，人流未有明顯減少，有人戴眼罩但徒手拿起鮮魚，亦有人輪流觸摸瓜菜，街市門口有人負責為入內人士量度體溫，但並不是時常當值，記者進入街市時，也沒有人負責量體溫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200725/photo/bkn-20200725125720774-0725_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200725170006\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200725%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200725125720774-0725_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200725170006&h=7f27eff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200725/bkn-20200725125720774-0725_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200725%2Fbkn-20200725125720774-0725_00822_001.html&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=bf3d5f44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200725/bkn-20200725125720774-0725_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"08785a9ea81f3df7a5597cef0cc04f3d8c211bae","tid":2124500,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317c1110ea92b0eaa2324afbcb707e58a0260a5b","tid":2124500,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT